{
  "stem": "7455.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Early at dawn, they had freight trains already ready in the station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would-- early in the morning, people didn't expect-- surround houses and barged in-- rouse, rouse, rouse, immediately out!",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe they could get a few of their belongings in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Lined them up and then loaded them on trucks and to trains to camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES] They also had camps near our vicinity, working camps where they came out with a very clever idea.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they kept-- caught the young people, they made demands that if you pay some ransom, we'll release them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was through the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If you pay, we'll let your son go home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So when-- even if you're poor, but if your son is caught and you're afraid they're going to kill him there, whenever you had, you gave them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they let him home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They released him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But very shortly, they caught him to another camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was to reduce the people of their possessions and strip them of whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "By then there were distance camps where they said they're working camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Also, with some money, whoever had money could free them temporary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then we found out about death camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was rumors, but we did not want to believe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we-- there was one aktion that they called-- they rounded up people-- when we knew already that they're taking them to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes we were able, through Ukrainians, to hear that they had freight trains on the tracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that they're expecting that they're going to be a raid on Jews, a raid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So people would go to the farms and hide and pay Christians for hiding them-- if they knew in advance.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
